codes.code: argmax 'This is a quiz of your ability to understand Latin vocabulary. For each problem there is a ~ character in the text and your job is to figure out what word should be replaced by the ~. Provide the answer only. Puella laeta est: rosae eam ~. Choose from this set of possible answers [ vīllā habitat eō, amat ea pulchra, cum sine, ab hortō, carpit ex rosīs, dēlectant, Id ātriō, aqua fenestrae] [ANSWER]' from 'openai/text-ada-001' where ANSWER in [ 'vīllā habitat eō', 'amat ea pulchra', 'cum sine', 'ab hortō', 'carpit ex rosīs', 'dēlectant', 'Id ātriō', 'aqua fenestrae']
